>\n另外, 喺通訊局度搵到自己大廈有FTTH(光纖入屋)<br />\n咁師傅嚟嗰陣我駛唔駛強調做FTTH, 以免佢做咗FTTB?</blockquote><br />\n定其實FTTH/FTTB唔會並存, 所以唔駛擔心呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以有齊兩款</blockquote><br />\n咁都係兜口兜面叫佢裝FTTH<br />\n免得裝錯日後DUM春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31389b7c477d76c44b746b6c08b432bf5a13eba9","tid":365362,"uid":15283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:04:43.000Z","msg":"點check而家用緊邊款"},{"pid":"2745afff3e0ad9468cd2af17b71b89bd30730dc0","tid":365362,"uid":80953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:51:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點check而家用緊邊款</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係用家, 講錯請其他巴打指正:<br />\n<br />\nFTTB: 喺牆度直接出條lan線畀你拮電腦/router<br />\nFTTH: 屋企會有個光纖盒"},{"pid":"1e0145f84113d3dcbb86bd6b111b7a7744519428","tid":365362,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T13:53:47.000Z","msg":"HKBN用光纖前後一啲分別都冇<br />\n反而多左個盒係到用電發熱"},{"pid":"87e3185a0ecf6a40d97241fad60e5ec16214149e","tid":365362,"uid":74368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T15:42:00.000Z","msg":"其實兩樣野咪一樣<br />\n一個係機房轉做lan線<br />\n一個屋企轉做lan線<br />\nlan線係咪都行到1000M"},{"pid":"93ec7069a5bac2f649ebf1e5c9c9301008a88168","tid":365362,"uid":33477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點check而家用緊邊款</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係用家, 講錯請其他巴打指正:<br />\n<br />\nFTTB: 喺牆度直接出條lan線畀你拮電腦/router<br />\nFTTH: 屋企會有個光纖盒</blockquote><br />\n所以一睇就分到FTTB同FTTH<br />\n簽約果陣睇實係FTTH就得"}]}